                </div>

                <h2 class="cd-text cd-title">feature tile with stickers</h2>
                <p class="cd-text">You can add a <a href="stickers">sticker</a> to a feature tile.</p>

                <div class="row">
                    <ul class="grid">
                        <li class="grid__col-xs-6 grid__col-sm-4">
