                <h1 class="cd-text cd-title">feature tile layouts</h1>
                <p class="cd-text">Feature tiles have various suggested layouts as shown here.</p>
                <h2 class="cd-title">square feature tile trio with text</h2>
                <h3 class="cd-title">image size: 450px x 450px</h3>
