        <div class="grid">
            <div class="grid__col-xs-12">
                <h2 class="cd-title">Feature banner</h2>
                <h3 class="cd-title">image size: 1200px x 300px</h3>
                <p class="cd-text">Feature banners are designed to work with an image that is 1200px wide and 300px high. For art direction you should consider two thirds of the image as the focus as demonstrated below. The content can be aligned left or right.</p>

                <img src="../images/banners/banner-template.jpg" class="img-responsive">
                <br>
                <img src="../images/banners/banner-template-right.jpg" class="img-responsive">
                <br>

                <h3 class="cd-title">with fade</h3>
                <p class="cd-text">Faded banner content will work for the vast majority of images and should be considered the default.</p>
                <div class="feature-banner" style="background-image:url('../images/banners/banner-berry.jpg');">
    <div class="feature-banner__content feature-banner__content--fade">
        <h2>good just got exciting</h2>
        <p class="lead">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Proin bibendum.</p>
        <a href="features#0" class="button button--primary button--continue button--lg button--block-xs">get started</a>
    </div>
</div>
