                <h2 class="cd-title">Feature images</h2>
                <h3 class="cd-title">image size: 1200px x (100 - 500px)</h3>
                <h3 class="cd-title">image only</h3>
                <p class="cd-text">Featured images can be used as headers for pages and should always include an alt property.</p>
                <img class="img-bleed" src="../images/feature/header-image.jpg" alt="give the gift of graze this christmas">
<pre class="hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-title">img</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">class</span>=<span class="hljs-value">"img-bleed"</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">src</span>=<span class="hljs-value">"/images/feature/header-image.jpg"</span> <span class="hljs-attribute">alt</span>=<span class="hljs-value">"give the gift of graze this christmas"</span>&gt;</span></pre>
